com.commander4j.db

Class JDBQMSelectList

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.commander4j.db.JDBQMSelectList

  • public class JDBQMSelectList
extends java.lang.Object
    The APP_QM_SELECTLIST table contains the lists which appear within the Quality Module results entry table. This table can contain multiple lists by use of a filter on a field called SELECT_LIST_ID

    See Also:
    JInternalFrameQMSelectListAdmin, JDialogQMSelectListProperties, JDBQMDictionary
